_:Nc9eaec1cccce41d5badf2e5d7150bbd1 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Kanishka Narayan was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology on 7 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Vale of Glamorgan in July 2024.</p>\n" .
